                            xaxis: {mode: 'time'},
                            yaxis: {
                                min: 4,
                                tickFormatter: function (v, axis) {
                                    var tier;
                                    var rank;
                                    if (v === 0) {
                                        tier = 0;
                                        rank = 0;
                                    } else if (v === 27) {
                                        tier = 9;
                                        rank = 1;
                                    } else if (v === 26) {
                                        tier = 8;
                                        rank = 1;
                                    } else if (v === 25) {
                                        tier = 7;
                                        rank = 1;
                                    } else if (v < 25 && v > 0) {
                                        tier = Math.ceil(v / 4);
                                        rank = 4 - (v - 1) % 4;
                                    } else {
                                        return '';
                                    }

                                    var rankStr;
                                    switch (rank) {
                                        case 0:
                                            rankStr = '';
                                            break;
                                        case 1:
                                            rankStr = 'I';
                                            break;
                                        case 2:
                                            rankStr = 'II';
                                            break;
                                        case 3:
                                            rankStr = 'III';
                                            break;
                                        case 4:
                                            rankStr = 'IV';
                                            break;
                                        case 5:
                                            rankStr = 'V';
                                            break;
                                    }
                                    return '<img src="//lolg-cdn.porofessor.gg/img/fond_sprite.png" class="leagueicons-24-' + tier + '-' + rank + '" width="24" height="24"> <div style="display:inline-block; width:8px; text-align: left">' + rankStr + '</div>';
                                },
                                tickDecimals: 0,
                            },
                            grid: toUseGrid
                        });
            } catch (e) {
                if (e.message.toString().indexOf("CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient") < 0) {
                    console.warn(e);
                }
            }
        }
    });

<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
    var graphGrid;
    var toUseGrid = graphGrid || {color: "#BBB", backgroundColor: "#FFF", borderWidth: 1, borderColor: "#E2E2E2"};

    graphFunctions.push(function () {
        var barChartData = [{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["1<!--0-->",38]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["2<!--1-->",30]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["3<!--2-->",26]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["4<!--3-->",20]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["5<!--4-->",16]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["6<!--5-->",15]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["7<!--6-->",8]]},{"color":"wgyellow","data":[["8<!--7-->",9]]}];
        barChartData.forEach((e) => e.color = window[e.color] || e.color); // In the case where the color is defined js side, we make sure we use it

        var placeholder = $("#graphDD8");
        if ($("#graphDD8").is(":visible")) {
            $.plot(placeholder, barChartData, {
                series: {
                    bars: {
                        show: true,
                        barWidth: 0.75,
                        align: "center"
                    }
                },
                xaxis: {
                    mode: "categories",
                    tickLength: 0
                },
                grid: toUseGrid,
            });
        }
    });
</script>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            $('#3starsCheckbox').change(function () {
                if (!!$(this).prop('checked')) {
                    $('.allTftChampions').css('display', 'none');
                    $('.lvl3TftChampions').css('display', 'table');
                } else {
                    $('.allTftChampions').css('display', 'table');
                    $('.lvl3TftChampions').css('display', 'none');
                }
                initProgressBars();
            });

        window.tooltipData = Object.assign(window.tooltipData, newTooltipData);

        window.tooltipData = newTooltipData;
    }
</script>                        </div>
